Black bean and avocado salad ðŸ¥‘

This is the perfect summer side salad or snack to have with corn chips!

Ingredients:
1 can (375g) black beans (rinsed and drained)
1 punnet of cherry tomatoes, diced
1 red onion, diced
2 avocados, diced
Coriander, sliced

Juice of 1 lime
Salt
Drizzle of olive oil

Add everything to a salad bowl.
Mix, serve and enjoy!

#saladrecipe #saladlover #healthysalad #summersalad #sidedish #saladsoftiktok #vegansalad #healthyrecipeideas
